snippet.textDisplay: I feel so bad but GLAD as well to have found Coke Studio... I started off with some not so Appealing songs that's y never followed thru Coke Studio.. But ever since I have come across Amit Trivedi and his compositions m amazed and literally binge watching every single song in this lockdown... I m listening to Shriram in Coke Studio first time as well. You know someone is a very good singer when even with a small piece they leave a Strong presence. Baari Baari and this Song.. The way Shriram sung his part was amazing...It was unique to him but still blended well with the song.... Amazing Amazing music.. This made me realize even more that the Bullywood biggies literally invest in trash music which is a remake of regional or old songs or just Huha music.... These songs deserve so much popularity...
